text: Laia Aubert (born 10 May 1986) is a Spanish cross-country skier. She competed in two events at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Spain Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Osona
